attributes.review: At first I thought it was just a normal app and nothing would go wrong but as soon as I downloaded it it asked if I wanted notifications on (said yea obviously) but then my phone SHUT OFF! I thought it died so I plugged it in, opened the app and then my phone crashed again. Turned on my phone and the app kept popping up then turning my phone off. I literally had to take it to the Sprint store to get fixed and they charged me over $100 for a replacement.  Please if you can DO NOT DOWNLOAD THIS APP! It will mess up your phone and it’s not worth it!!!
